{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"使用 ARIA：角色、状态和属性","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>ARIA 定义了可以应用于元素的语义，这些语义分为 <strong>roles</strong>（定义一种用户界面元素）、<strong>states</strong> 和 <strong>properties</strong>，这些都是角色所支持的。作者必须在元素的生命周期中为其分配一个 ARIA 角色和适当的状态和属性，除非该元素已经具有适当的 ARIA 语义（通过使用适当的 HTML 元素）。添加 ARIA 语义只会向浏览器的无障碍 API 公开额外信息，而不会影响页面的 DOM。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"角色","title":"角色","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"组件角色","title":"组件角色","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/button_role\">button</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/checkbox_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">checkbox (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/gridcell_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">gridcell (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/link_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">link (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li>menuitem</li>\n  <li>menuitemcheckbox</li>\n  <li>menuitemradio</li>\n  <li>option</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/progressbar_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">progressbar (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/radio_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">radio (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li>scrollbar</li>\n  <li>searchbox</li>\n  <li>separator (when focusable)</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/slider_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">slider (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li>spinbutton</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/switch_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">switch (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/tab_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tab (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/tabpanel_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabpanel (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/textbox_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">textbox (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li>treeitem</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"复合角色","title":"复合角色","isH3":true,"content":"<p>下面的技术描述了每个复合角色及其必需和可选的子角色。</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>combobox</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/grid_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid (en-US)</a> (包含 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/row_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">row (en-US)</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/gridcell_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">gridcell (en-US)</a>, rowheader, columnheader)</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/listbox_role\">listbox</a> (包含 option)</li>\n  <li>menu</li>\n  <li>menubar</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/radio_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">radiogroup (en-US)</a> (参考 radio)</li>\n  <li>tablist (包含 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/tab_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tab (en-US)</a> 和 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/tabpanel_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabpanel (en-US)</a>)</li>\n  <li>tree</li>\n  <li>treegrid</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"文档结构角色","title":"文档结构角色","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/application_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">application (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/article_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">article (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/cell_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">cell (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li>columnheader</li>\n  <li>definition</li>\n  <li>directory</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/document_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">document (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li>feed</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/figure_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">figure (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/group_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">group (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/heading_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">heading (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/Role_Img\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">img</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/List_role\">list</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/Listitem_role\">listitem</a></li>\n  <li>math</li>\n  <li>none</li>\n  <li>note</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/presentation_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">presentation (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/row_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">row (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/rowgroup_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">rowgroup (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li>rowheader</li>\n  <li>separator</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/table_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">table (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li>term</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/toolbar_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">toolbar (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li>tooltip</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"具有里程碑意义的角色","title":"具有里程碑意义的角色","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/banner_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">banner (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/complementary_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">complementary (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/contentinfo_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">contentinfo (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/form_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">form (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/main_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">main (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/navigation_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">navigation (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/